            <p class="center">
                <img
                    src={Ava.src}
                    alt="Talal Emran"
                    width="500px"
                    style="border-radius: 5%; width: 300px; height: 337px; object-fit: cover;"
                />
            </p>
            <h1>
                Talal Emran, Web Designer, Developer, Graphic Designer and
                Photographer
            </h1>
            <p>
                Hi 👋, my name is Talal Emran. I'm a web designer and
                photographer. I have been doing website development for more
                than 10 years.
            </p>
            <p>
                My goal is to create a website that is easy to use and looks
                great. I have experience in HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and
                WordPress.
            </p>
            <p>
                In addition to web design, I also have a passion for
                photography.
            </p>
            <br />
            <hr />
            <br />
            <h2>Last Projects</h2>
            <p>
                <ul class="list-none">
